snippet.title: A New Kaizo Era: Newer Demo Trailer
snippet.description:
The demo is out NOW: https://youtu.be/7CsOKX6C-Qk

It's been really long since I've released anything from my hack, and the hack's scope has massively evolved since the old trailers on my channel so it's time for a new demo. It's decently close to finished, I just need to tie up the loose ends which might take me some time, so it's scheduled to release some time next month.

NSMBW Kaizo Discord: https://discord.gg/CyXpvZj

The song is Heat Haze Shadow from Tekken 7: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=COBzBGSIny0
